      "type": "text",
      "x": 2863.1799865205126,
      "y": -4049.0381672637886,
      "width": 522,
      "height": 75,
      "text": "Jesse 在 v5.0.6 release notes 中明确说：\n\"do not modify carefully-tuned content (Red Flags tables, rationalization lists,\n'human partner' language) without evidence the change is an improvement\"\n——这种语言不可乱改",
      "originalText": "Jesse 在 v5.0.6 release notes 中明确说：\n\"do not modify carefully-tuned content (Red Flags tables, rationalization lists,\n'human partner' language) without evidence the change is an improvement\"\n——这种语言不可乱改",
