      "text": "这 6 个原则对 LLM 有可测量的统计显著影响 — 不是凭主观感觉",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这 6 个原则对 LLM 有可测量的统计显著影响 — 不是凭主观感觉",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "index": "a00000575",
      "autoResize": true
    },
    {
      "id": "S18_wh-t3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 423.7468027495772,
      "y": 2210.090474690889,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 56,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a8a",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "S18_fr1",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 7004,
      "version": 1185,
      "versionNonce": 1133350607,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778224717548,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "• 统计显著 — 有数据支撑，非主观感觉\n• 可量化测量 — 效果可被客观验证\n• 完整覆盖 — 六大原则对 LLM 均有可测效应",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• 统计显著 — 有数据支撑，非主观感觉\n• 可量化测量 — 效果可被客观验证\n• 完整覆盖 — 六大原则对 LLM 均有可测效应",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 11,
      "index": "a00000576",
      "autoResize": true
    },
