      "type": "text",
      "x": 111.77237181682176,
      "y": 12164.97571374545,
      "width": 254,
      "height": 238,
      "text": "Claude 在 task 中检测到\n「未测试的代码已存在」\n\n✗ 不允许「保留作参考」\n✗ 不允许「边写边测」\n✗ 不允许「adapt 后再测」\n\n➜  必须删除代码\n➜  重新走 RED→GREEN\n    →REFACTOR 流程",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#7c2d12",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
