      "type": "text",
      "x": 701.7723718168218,
      "y": 12164.97571374545,
      "width": 264,
      "height": 238,
      "text": "Cialdini 承诺一致性原理\n+ 反向利用 Sunk Cost\n\n一旦已写了代码\n「删除」的痛感\n远比「提醒」强得多\n\n→ Claude 主动避免再犯\n→ 约束 = 行为执行机制\n   不是提醒，是强制",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#164e63",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
