      "seed": 111012,
      "version": 1345,
      "versionNonce": 676800417,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778225369491,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "「Delete means delete / Don't look at it」\n绝对化语言不给侥幸保留留口子\n→ 堵住所有自我合理化空间\n→ 无模糊地带 = 无绕过机会",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "「Delete means delete / Don't look at it」\n绝对化语言不给侥幸保留留口子\n→ 堵住所有自我合理化空间\n→ 无模糊地带 = 无绕过机会",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a0000066"
