      "versionNonce": 383082305,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1778225369491,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "写「请用 TDD」→ Claude 答「好的」\n→ 写代码时忘了\n提醒不触发任何行为锁定\n无心理代价 = 无约束力",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "写「请用 TDD」→ Claude 答「好的」\n→ 写代码时忘了\n提醒不触发任何行为锁定\n无心理代价 = 无约束力",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "a00000663"
    },
