      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "text": "\"Do NOT invoke any implementation skill\nuntil you have presented a design\nand the user has approved it.\"\n→ 不点头，Claude 不准写一行代码",
